Package: chumby-player-data
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Jan <jan@simula.no>
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Description: Chumby control panel data (fixtures, SWFs)
 Fixture tree (canned chumby.com/native responses, virtual rootfs,
 widget SWFs) and controlpanel.swf for chumby-player.
 .
 PRIVATE USE ONLY: controlpanel.swf and the widget SWFs are copyrighted
 chumby firmware. This package must never be published in an apt repo.
 .
 The player copies fixtures/ to /var/lib/chumby on first run; after
 upgrading this package, remove /var/lib/chumby/fixtures to re-seed
 (this discards panel-made settings: alarms, streams, volume).
